{
  "texts": [
    "However, the present paper is not the only outcome of our discussions.",
    "Notably, most participants found the process itself highly rewarding, not least because these discussions have tremendously increased our knowledge of the literature and our mutual understanding of alternative theoretical positions.",
    "Looking back at this arduous effort and forward to how much more could be done in both depth and scope, what we have achieved feels like a first tiny step though not lacking flaws.",
    "Nevertheless, we believe and hope that this paper will catalyze scientific progress and so be of high value for the visual-distraction community and beyond.",
    "As the ancient Chinese saying goes: \"A journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step.\""
  ]
}